profile:
Nufloors Coquitlam has been serving the tri city residents since 1986.  As a second generation family run business, we pride ourselves on community, commitment, service, product, warranty and our team.  Over half of our staff has been with us for over 28 years!

We are proud to be a member of the BBB with an outstanding A+ rating for a solid 26 years.  We are also one of 3 Shaw Design Centers in the Lower Mainland.  As a recently renovated Shaw Design Center, we offer a full line of Shaw carpet, hardwood, laminate and vinyl, as well we carry over 15 other supply brands to suit whatever your flooring needs are.

We are a full service store, with warranties on all labour and installation, and have the largest selection of product from manufactures that have LEED and sustainability at the forefront of their business.  We have the widest selection of products with no VOC’s, something that is important to many people in today’s world.

Our showroom has carpet, hardwood, both engineered and solid, laminate, vinyl, VCT, LVT, vinyl plank, cork, area rugs, roll ends and a full commercial line up as well.  Our staff is experienced, knowledgeable, respectful and will provide you with advice that is right for you and your home and family needs.

We support our community by supporting local businesses for our business needs; as well we support local minor hockey and soccer throughout the year.  We hope to continue the tradition as we start another 28 years and beyond.

Our experts are happy to assist you with your flooring questions.
